## Testing Strategy

### Mock Testing
- Test with mock adapters during development
- Simulate various response scenarios (success, failure, timeout)
- Test webhook handling with mock payloads

### Real Testing
- Use sandbox/test environments for real providers
- Test with small amounts for payment gateways
- Monitor webhook delivery and processing

## Security Considerations

### Mock Phase
- Use test data only
- No real credentials in code
- Mock signatures and verification

### Real Phase
- Secure credential management
- Signature verification for webhooks
- Rate limiting and monitoring
- Error handling and retry logic
